responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "596A608740F3C2939E0FCBAC0A1C60F1", "Fates be told, if it isn\'t Carlotta\'s beguiler. My sources say you\'ve been subverting curses and hiring occultists. It seems the war against goblin-kind holds fast against the sorcerers\' fiercest spells.")
